text: Kilian Le Blouch (born 7 October 1989) is a French judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 66 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the third round by An Baul. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:French male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of France Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:European Games competitors for France Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in judo Category:European Games bronze medalists for France Category:People from Clamart
